10:
We went to a farming village the
other day after taking on a request
from the Guild, and the villagers
gave us some food.
12:
But... it's way too much for us.
Apparently these are high-quality
carrots, though.
16:
Special Week. Would you like to help
us with eating them?
24:
You can eat all of them if you want. I
definitely won't be having any more.
27:
I've been eating carrot dishes
nonstop recently... I even dreamed
about it last night...
31:
Whoa! Dreaming of carrots? That's
wonderful!
35:
I love carrots! If you wouldn't mind,
I'd be happy to eat them!
39: Phew... That was great. I'm stuffed.
42:
I-I didn't think you'd actually eat all
of them! But... you really helped us
out.
46:
Th-that said... Are you feeling all
right? Your stomach looks as though
it could burst from all the carrots
inside...
51:
Yes, I'm fine! My belly often ends up
looking like this after a big meal.
58:
Thanks for eating so much of my
cooking today. I had a lot of fun
cooking for you.
64:
Not at all! Thanks for everything
today, including the food!
75:
Hmm? You seem sort of down
today. Did something happen?
84:
What's up? You put on weight or
something?
93:
Lucky guess? Well, that's what
happens when you stuff your face
like that.
97:
I'm not so sure. At a glance, she
doesn't look any different.
102:
Ooh... It would make a huge
difference in a race, though...
106: Ah, right. You're kinda like an athlete.
111:
Yes... So I'm on a diet now. It's pretty
tough, though...
115:
I see... I wish there was something
we could do to help.
119:
Perhaps I could help you with a
low-calorie diet? I doubt I could help
more than the folks at Tracen
Academy, though...
122:
Oh, but... Maybe we could help take
your mind off things in a different
way?
134:
We're in something called a VR
machine. Here, you can experience
a great deal of things within a virtual
space.
138:
You can even experience taste in
here, and you don't have to worry
about gaining weight because you
aren't actually eating anything!
147: Indeed! Eat to your heart's content.
155:
Wowww! I-it's amazing! I can really
taste it... Even the texture is right!
159:
Mmm-mm! Super tasty! I never
could've imagined eating like this
while still losing weight!
162:
...O-oh? I keep eating, but I don't feel
even a little bit more full...
167:
Yeah, because you're not actually
eating anything.
178:
S-sorry... I think we just made you
even hungrier...
182:
Uhh... What else could we do to help
take her mind off things...
191:
It's a recreation of one of your
memories. Don't worry, we can't see
anything.
193:
I get the feeling you're seeing
something that motivates you...
Right?
204:
Yeah... Nobody runs like Suzuka
does...
208:
...Thank you very much, everyone.
I'm feeling super pumped up now!
211:
I'll do everything I can to be able to
run with Suzuka...
217:
Hey everyone! Thanks for everything
you did for me the other day!
221:
Oh, hey there. Have you been feeling
all right since then?
225:
I sure have! Thanks to you, I've
returned to my normal weight and
I'm in perfect condition to race!
230:
I'm happy to hear that. We wish you
nothing but success.
236:
Someone gave this to me after a
job. It's their new carrot cake.
240:
You like these, right? You can have it
if you want.
243:
I-I love carrot cake! B-but... If I eat it,
I'll be right back to where I started!
248:
Ah... Don't worry. We'll save it for you.
Let's enjoy it together after your
race, okay?
252:
R-really?! In that case, I'll make sure
to win the next race, and then we
can really celebrate!
256: All righty! I'm ready and rar'n to go!
